<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
Reply <a href="/eq/board/message?board.id=shamanbalance&message.id=5239#M5239">26</a> of 109
</span>

			<br><img src="/i/p.gif" width=1 height=6><br>
			<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
			
					Viewed 542 times<br>
					
			</span>
			
		</td>
		
		<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	
		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV>I could not agree with aggememnon more;&nbsp;slow is not a factor.&nbsp; The mob will always be slowed.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;We have needed a boost to our healing for a long time.&nbsp; Right now you can grab any of the 3 tank types for a group, you can grab any of the 3 slowers for a group, but you can't grab any of the 3 healers, not at the higher end of the game.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I loved playing my shaman in the lower end game, I was able to act as a slower, or a healer, or just do damage with my dots.&nbsp; Now I am 3rd&nbsp;pick for a slower, my dps isn't worth mention, and If I am being asked to go anywhere above sol ro, I will not be asked to come and heal.&nbsp;&nbsp;My suggestion is give druids a boost to healing, put shamans where druids used to be, and make us all happy.&nbsp; Clerics will be, and should be the main healer type,&nbsp;but clerics are not always available.&nbsp; We need more&nbsp;options when making groups.&nbsp;&nbsp;The&nbsp;best way would be to make it so that you can pick any of the 3 tanks, any of the 3 healers, any of the 3 slowers and make a good group.&nbsp; Fill the last 3 slots with&nbsp;one of the 3 pullers and 2 dps classes and your ready to go.&nbsp; More time having fun and less headach searching the LFG tool for a cleric.&nbsp; The solution to this has nothing to do with our ability to slow.&nbsp; The mob will be slowed 99% of the time, unless it is unslowable.&nbsp; What should be taken into consideration is our ability to get back mana fast.&nbsp; Give us higher casting cost to balance it out.&nbsp;&nbsp; We need an all around bost to our healing, not just when the mob is unslowable.&nbsp; </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Kelroahg</DIV>
<DIV>68 shammy </DIV>
<DIV>Morell Thule</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>	
		</td></tr>
