<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
Reply <a href="/eq/board/message?board.id=shamanbalance&message.id=5247#M5247">34</a> of 109
</span>

			<br><img src="/i/p.gif" width=1 height=6><br>
			<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
			
					Viewed 506 times<br>
					
